<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>STEAL MY FACE — Game Design Document v3</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unbounded:wght@400;600;800;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

:root{
  --void:#06060e;
  --panel:#0e0e1c;
  --panel2:#131326;
  --ink:#eceaf4;
  --muted:#8c8aa6;
  --line:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  --fire:#ff4f0a;
  --ember:#ff8b00;
  --volt:#3d88ff;
  --psy:#a855f7;
  --gold:#ffb800;
  --mint:#00ffb2;
  --div:#ff44ff;
  --common:#9a9aa8;
  --ok:#3ddc6a;
  --warn:#ffb800;
  --bug:#ff4d5e;
}

*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--void);
  color:var(--ink);
  font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
  font-size:16px;
  line-height:1.65;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
::selection{background:var(--fire);color:#fff}

/* ====== fond atmosphérique ====== */
body::before{
  content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:-2;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 45% at 15% 0%,rgba(255,79,10,.09),transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 40% at 88% 12%,rgba(168,85,247,.08),transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% 105%,rgba(61,136,255,.07),transparent 60%);
}
body::after{
  content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:-1;pointer-events:none;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.012) 1px,transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.012) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:48px 48px;
}

/* ====== barre de progression ====== */
#progress{
  position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:3px;width:0%;z-index:100;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--fire),var(--ember),var(--gold));
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,79,10,.8);
}

.wrap{max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}

/* ====== HERO ====== */
header.hero{
  min-height:100svh;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;
  text-align:center;padding:90px 20px 70px;
}
.sky{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none}
.meteor{
  position:absolute;top:-12%;
  width:3px;height:130px;border-radius:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,var(--c,#ff8b00) 55%,#fff);
  filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(--c,#ff8b00));
  transform:rotate(33deg);
  animation:fall var(--d,5s) linear infinite;
  animation-delay:var(--del,0s);
  opacity:0;
}
@keyframes fall{
  0%{transform:translate(0,0) rotate(33deg);opacity:0}
  6%{opacity:1}
  78%{opacity:1}
  100%{transform:translate(-60vh,110vh) rotate(33deg);opacity:0}
}
.impact-glow{
  position:absolute;bottom:-14%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:130vw;height:38vh;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center,rgba(255,79,10,.22),rgba(255,79,10,.05) 45%,transparent 70%);
  animation:breathe 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  pointer-events:none;
}
@keyframes breathe{0%,100%{opacity:.7}50%{opacity:1}}

.hero .eyebrow{
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.45em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ember);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,139,0,.35);border-radius:100px;
  padding:9px 20px;background:rgba(255,79,10,.06);margin-bottom:34px;
  position:relative;z-index:2;
}
h1.title{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:900;
  font-size:clamp(2.4rem,9vw,6.8rem);line-height:.98;letter-spacing:-.01em;
  position:relative;z-index:2;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff 8%,#ffd9a0 38%,var(--ember) 62%,var(--fire) 100%);
  background-size:100% 200%;
  -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;
  animation:shimmer 7s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes shimmer{0%,100%{background-position:50% 0%}50%{background-position:50% 38%}}
.hero .tagline{
  margin-top:26px;max-width:640px;font-size:clamp(1.05rem,2.4vw,1.4rem);
  font-weight:300;color:var(--muted);position:relative;z-index:2;
}
.hero .tagline strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}

.stats{
  display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;
  margin-top:52px;position:relative;z-index:2;
}
.stat{
  background:rgba(14,14,28,.7);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;
  padding:18px 26px;min-width:128px;backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
}
.stat b{
  display:block;font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
  font-size:1.9rem;color:#fff;line-height:1.1;
}
.stat span{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.66rem;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
.scroll-cue{
  position:absolute;bottom:26px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--muted);
  animation:bob 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;z-index:2;
}
@keyframes bob{0%,100%{transform:translate(-50%,0)}50%{transform:translate(-50%,8px)}}

/* ====== SOMMAIRE ====== */
nav.toc{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;
  padding:30px 32px;margin:-50px auto 80px;position:relative;z-index:3;
}
nav.toc h2{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.15rem;
  letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:18px;color:var(--ember);
}
.toc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:8px}
.toc-grid a{
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;
  color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;font-size:.92rem;
  padding:9px 12px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid transparent;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.toc-grid a:hover,.toc-grid a:focus-visible{background:rgba(255,79,10,.07);border-color:rgba(255,79,10,.25);color:var(--ember)}
.toc-grid a::before{
  content:attr(data-n);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--fire);
}

/* ====== CHAPITRES ====== */
section{margin-bottom:110px;scroll-margin-top:40px}
.ch-head{margin-bottom:34px}
.ch-eyebrow{
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.32em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c,var(--fire));margin-bottom:12px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.ch-eyebrow::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--c,var(--fire)),transparent);min-width:40px}
.ch-head h2{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
  font-size:clamp(1.5rem,4.2vw,2.5rem);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
section p{color:#c6c4d6;margin-bottom:16px;max-width:820px}
section strong{color:var(--ink)}
h3{font-size:1.18rem;font-weight:700;margin:30px 0 12px;color:var(--ember)}

/* badges */
.badge{
  display:inline-block;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;
  padding:4px 11px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;
  vertical-align:middle;margin-left:8px;
}
.b-ok{background:rgba(61,220,106,.12);color:var(--ok);border:1px solid rgba(61,220,106,.35)}
.b-wip{background:rgba(255,184,0,.12);color:var(--warn);border:1px solid rgba(255,184,0,.35)}
.b-todo{background:rgba(140,138,166,.12);color:var(--muted);border:1px solid rgba(140,138,166,.3)}
.b-bug{background:rgba(255,77,94,.12);color:var(--bug);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,94,.35)}

/* cartes & callouts */
.callout{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,79,10,.08),rgba(168,85,247,.05));
  border:1px solid rgba(255,79,10,.22);border-radius:16px;
  padding:20px 24px;margin:22px 0;font-size:.95rem;max-width:820px;
}
.callout .ct{
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.64rem;letter-spacing:.2em;
  color:var(--fire);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;
}

/* tables */
table{
  width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:18px 0 8px;font-size:.9rem;
  background:var(--panel);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;
}
th{
  background:var(--panel2);color:var(--ember);text-align:left;
  padding:12px 15px;font-weight:600;font-size:.72rem;
  text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
td{padding:11px 15px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:#c6c4d6;vertical-align:top}
tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.table-scroll{overflow-x:auto;border-radius:14px}

/* ====== boucle de gameplay : timeline ====== */
.loop{position:relative;margin-top:36px;padding-left:34px;max-width:760px}
.loop::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;left:11px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--fire),var(--psy),var(--volt));
  opacity:.45;
}
.loop-step{position:relative;padding:0 0 26px 22px}
.loop-step::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;left:-30px;top:5px;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--void);border:3px solid var(--fire);
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,79,10,.6);
}
.loop-step b{color:var(--ink)}
.loop-step span{color:var(--muted);font-size:.95rem}

/* ====== raretés ====== */
.tiers{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(135px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-top:28px}
.tier{
  --tc:#fff;
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;
  padding:18px 16px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  transition:transform .25s,box-shadow .25s,border-color .25s;
}
.tier::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
  background:var(--tc);box-shadow:0 0 14px var(--tc);
}
.tier:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);border-color:var(--tc);box-shadow:0 14px 34px -14px var(--tc)}
.tier h4{font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--tc);letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:10px}
.tier .row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);padding:3px 0;border-top:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.07)}
.tier .row b{color:var(--ink);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:600}

/* ====== masques ====== */
.mask-tier{margin-bottom:26px}
.mask-tier-title{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;letter-spacing:.06em;
  margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:12px;border-left:4px solid var(--tc,#fff);color:var(--tc,#fff);
}
.mask-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(155px,1fr));gap:10px}
.chip{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:11px;
  padding:11px 14px;font-size:.88rem;transition:border-color .2s,transform .2s;
}
.chip:hover{border-color:var(--tc,rgba(255,255,255,.25));transform:translateY(-2px)}
.chip .mn{font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);display:block}
.chip .mp{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* ====== jauge de vol — pièce signature ====== */
.gauge-demo{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;
  padding:34px 30px;margin:30px 0;max-width:640px;
  box-shadow:0 0 60px -25px rgba(255,79,10,.4);
}
.gauge-title{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.06em;
  text-align:center;margin-bottom:18px;transition:color .3s;
}
.gauge{display:flex;gap:7px;height:34px}
.seg{
  flex:1;border-radius:7px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
  transition:background .3s,box-shadow .3s;
}
.seg.full{
  background:var(--segc,var(--ember));
  box-shadow:0 0 14px var(--segc,var(--ember));
  border-color:transparent;
}
.gauge-sub{
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:14px;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.66rem;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--muted);
}

/* ====== évolution ====== */
.evo{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(190px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:30px}
.evo-card{
  --ec:#888;
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;
  padding:24px 20px;text-align:center;position:relative;
}
.evo-card .orb{
  width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 16px;
  background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%,#fff3,transparent 40%),var(--ec);
  box-shadow:0 0 26px var(--ec);
  animation:orb 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes orb{0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.1)}}
.evo-card h4{font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ec)}
.evo-card .mult{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:1.5rem;color:#fff;margin:8px 0 4px}
.evo-card small{color:var(--muted);font-size:.78rem;display:block}

/* ====== boutique ====== */
.shop{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(235px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:26px}
.shop-item{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;
  transition:transform .2s,border-color .2s;
}
.shop-item:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:rgba(255,139,0,.4)}
.shop-item h4{font-weight:700;font-size:.98rem;margin-bottom:4px}
.shop-item .price{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:8px}
.shop-item p{font-size:.84rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px}
.shop-item .badge{margin-left:0}

/* ====== roadmap ====== */
.wave{
  display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;
  padding:20px 22px;margin-bottom:12px;
}
.wave .wn{
  font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.05rem;
  color:var(--fire);min-width:50px;
}
.wave h4{font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:3px}
.wave p{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;max-width:none}

/* ====== reveal au scroll ====== */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}

footer{
  text-align:center;padding:70px 24px 90px;color:var(--muted);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.74rem;letter-spacing:.06em;
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:30px;line-height:2;
}

@media (max-width:640px){
  .stats{gap:8px}
  .stat{padding:13px 16px;min-width:96px}
  .stat b{font-size:1.4rem}
  nav.toc{margin-top:-30px;padding:22px}
  section{margin-bottom:78px}
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
  *,*::before,*::after{animation:none!important;transition:none!important}
  .reveal{opacity:1;transform:none}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress"></div>

<!-- ====================== HERO ====================== -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="sky" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="meteor" style="left:18%;--c:#ff8b00;--d:5.5s;--del:0s"></span>
    <span class="meteor" style="left:42%;--c:#a855f7;--d:7s;--del:2.1s"></span>
    <span class="meteor" style="left:64%;--c:#3d88ff;--d:6s;--del:3.4s"></span>
    <span class="meteor" style="left:81%;--c:#ffb800;--d:8s;--del:1.2s"></span>
    <span class="meteor" style="left:30%;--c:#ff44ff;--d:9s;--del:5s"></span>
    <span class="meteor" style="left:92%;--c:#ff4f0a;--d:6.5s;--del:4.2s"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="impact-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="eyebrow">Game Design Document · v3 · Juin 2026</div>
  <h1 class="title">STEAL<br>MY FACE</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Trouve un masque rare. <strong>Garde-le</strong> pendant que tout le serveur essaie de te le voler.</p>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat"><b data-count="33">0</b><span>masques</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><b data-count="27">0</b><span>pouvoirs</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><b data-count="7">0</b><span>raretés</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><b data-count="16">0</b><span>joueurs max</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-cue">▼ SCROLL</div>
</header>

<div class="wrap">

<!-- ====================== SOMMAIRE ====================== -->
<nav class="toc reveal">
  <h2>Sommaire</h2>
  <div class="toc-grid">
    <a href="#vision" data-n="01">Vision &amp; Pitch</a>
    <a href="#boucle" data-n="02">Boucle de gameplay</a>
    <a href="#meteorites" data-n="03">Météorites</a>
    <a href="#masques" data-n="04">Masques &amp; raretés</a>
    <a href="#pouvoirs" data-n="05">Les 27 pouvoirs</a>
    <a href="#fusion" data-n="06">Fusion</a>
    <a href="#vol" data-n="07">Système de vol</a>
    <a href="#mobilite" data-n="08">Inventaire &amp; mobilité</a>
    <a href="#evolution" data-n="09">Évolution</a>
    <a href="#economie" data-n="10">Économie</a>
    <a href="#boutique" data-n="11">Boutique</a>
    <a href="#retention" data-n="12">Rétention</a>
    <a href="#monetisation" data-n="13">Monétisation</a>
    <a href="#roadmap" data-n="14">Roadmap</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ====================== 01 VISION ====================== -->
<section id="vision" class="reveal">
  <div class="ch-head">
    <div class="ch-eyebrow">Chapitre 01 — Vision</div>
    <h2>Une cible vivante qui rapporte gros</h2>
  </div>
  <p><strong>Steal My Face</strong> est un PvP nerveux pour 12 à 16 joueurs sur une ville nocturne de 600×600 studs baignée de néons. Des météorites font tomber des masques de rareté variable. Tu en équipes un : il génère du <strong>Face Cash</strong> en continu — et tout le serveur sait que tu le portes.</p>
  <p>La tension naît de la possession. Plus ton masque est rare, plus il rapporte, plus il attire les convoitises. Le joueur vit un cycle permanent de prise de risque : garder un masque précieux le plus longtemps possible, esquiver, fuir, contre-attaquer.</p>
  <div class="callout">
    <div class="ct">Expérience recherchée</div>
    « Ce mec porte un masque Divin depuis 3 minutes, il rapporte une fortune — il faut l'arrêter. » Chaque porteur ressent l'adrénaline d'être traqué. Chaque voleur ressent celle de la chasse.
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================== 02 BOUCLE ====================== -->
<section id="boucle" class="reveal">
  <div class="ch-head" style="--c:var(--volt)">
    <div class="ch-eyebrow" style="--c:var(--volt)">Chapitre 02 — Boucle de gameplay</div>
    <h2>Le cycle qui ne s'arrête jamais</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="loop">
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Une météorite tombe</b><br><span>Annonce, traînée de feu, cercle d'avertissement coloré selon la rareté.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Un masque apparaît à l'impact</b><br><span>Rareté tirée selon le type de météorite. Cratère + explosion.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Ramassage par proximité</b><br><span>Le masque se place sur le visage et part dans l'inventaire.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Le masque génère du Face Cash</b><br><span>Chaque seconde, selon rareté × stade d'évolution.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Les autres attaquent</b><br><span>Chaque coup remplit la jauge de vol du porteur.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Le porteur survit</b><br><span>Fuite, dash, double saut, blink, pouvoir du masque.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Le masque évolue</b><br><span>×1.5 → ×2.5 → ×5 sur le cash, aura DBZ visible par tous.</span></div>
    <div class="loop-step"><b>Jauge pleine = masque au sol</b><br><span>Il redevient disponible pour tous. Le cycle recommence.</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================== 03 MÉTÉORITES ====================== -->
<section id="meteorites" class="reveal">
  <div class="ch-head" style="--c:var(--ember)">
    <div class="ch-eyebrow" style="--c:var(--ember)">Chapitre 03 — Météorites <span class="badge b-ok">Opérationnel</span></div>
    <h2>Trois pluies, trois enjeux</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="table-scroll">
  <table>
    <tr><th>Type</th><th>Fréquence</th><th>Avertissement</th><th>Table de rareté</th></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Normale</strong></td><td>45–60 s</td><td>5 s</td><td>Commun 40 · Rare 30 · Épique 16 · Légendaire 8 · Mythique 4 · Ultime 1.5 · Divin 0.5 (%)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Spéciale</strong></td><td>8–10 min</td><td>15 s + annonce serveur</td><td>Mythique 60 · Ultime 28 · Divin 12 (%)</td></tr>
